title: VIZLEXIA - A VHS ODYSSEY
description:
A warped trip from 1955 all the way through to 2018 in 46 minutes - tearing through old TV broadcasts, scratched DVDs, unravelled VHS tapes and even a broken Laserdisc™ or two. 

Featuring footage from old educational tapes, recorded TV shows, YouTube tutorials, VHS misfits, glitched out sports broadcasts and blockbusters to present Vizlexia.
